{"title":"中国世纪［外一首］","authors":["毛翰"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"［外一首］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛翰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内忧外患都曾经过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山与长城依旧巍峨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中华百年一梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的大业后有来者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦屈辱都曾经过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河与长江依旧执著。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中华千年一梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州不改汉唐气魄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙飞凤舞是永远的图腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣与梦想召唤着你我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让历史预言让未来承诺："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十一世纪属于中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归字谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄你一枝二月兰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月兰乡是家园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山中的杜鹃水边的燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相问游子何时还？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄你一枝湘妃竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘妃夜夜歌如哭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月的龙舟六月的浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘妃望断天涯路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄你一枝重阳菊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重阳最是伤心日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老父的白发老母的泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方的儿女长别离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄你一枝陇头梅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花三弄雪花飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一年风光老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯游子你何不归？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}